sp_whoisactive SQL Server Monitoring Stored Procedure by Adam Machanic 
         sp_whoisactive 
         
        sp_whoisactive is a comprehensive activity monitoring stored procedure that works for all versions of SQL Server from 2005 through 2017.
         
        You can find the most recent versions on the  Downloads  page.
         
        Documentation is available on the  Documentation  page.
         
         Subscribe  to the super-low-volume (once a quarter, max) sp_whoisactive email list: 
 
     
	
 
